keyMappings:
map o Vomnibar.activate keyword=dd
map t Vomnibar.activateInNewTab keyword=dd
map D passNextKey
# switch the bindings around to move tabs
map J nextTab
map K previousTab
unmap r
searchEngines:
dd: https://duckduckgo.com/?q=%s DuckDuckGo
r: https://duckduckgo.com/?q=%s%20site%3Areddit.com DDG+Reddit
y: https://www.youtube.com/results?search_query=%s YouTube
gh: https://github.com/snprajwal/%s My GitHub
